: {{Whig Party (United States)/meta/color}}\" |{{color|white|18}}\n|[[Samuel Dickinson Hubbard]]\n|[[Connecticut]]\n|August 31, 1852\n|Fillmore\n|-\n! style=\"background: {{Democratic Party (United States)/meta/color}};\" |{{color|white|19}}\n|[[James Campbell (Postmaster General)|James Campbell]]\n|[[Pennsylvania]]\n|March 7, 1853\n|[[Franklin Pierce|Pierce]]\n|-\n! style=\"background: {{Democratic Party (United States)/meta/color}};\" |{{color|white|20}}\n|[[Aaron V. Brown]]\n|[[Tennessee]]\n|March 6, 1857\n|[[James Buchanan|Buchanan]]\n|-\n! style=\"background: {{Republican Party (United States)/meta/color}};\" |{{color|white|21}}\n|[[Joseph Holt]]\n|[[Kentucky]]\n|March 14, 1859\n|Buchanan\n|-\n! style=\"background: {{Democratic Party (United States)/meta/color}};\" |{{color|white|22}}\n|[[Horatio King]]\n|[[Maine]]\n|February 12, 1861\n|Buchanan\n|-\n! style=\"background: {{Republican Party (United States)/meta/color}};\" |{{color|white|23}}\n|[[Montgomery Blair]]\n|[[District of Columbia]]\n|March 5, 1861\n|[[Abraham Lincoln|Lincoln]]\n|-\n! style=\"background: {{Republican Party (United States)/meta/color}};\" |{{color|white|24}}\n|[[William Dennison (Ohio governor)|William Dennison]]\n|[[Ohio]]\n|September 24, 1864\n|Lincoln, [[Andrew Johnson|A. Johnson]]\n|-\n! style=\"background: {{Republican Party (United States)/meta/color}};\" |{{color|white|25}}\n|[[Alexander W. Randall]]\n|[[Wisconsin]]\n|July 25, 1866\n|A. Johnson\n|-\n! style=\"background: {{Republican Party (United States)/meta/color}};\" |{{color|white|26}}\n|[[John A. J. Creswell]]\n|[[Maryland]]\n|March 5, 1869\n|[[Ulysses S. Grant|Grant]]\n|-\n! style=\"background: {{Republican Party (United States)/meta/color}};\" |{{color|white|27}}\n|[[James William Marshall|James W. Marshall]]\n|[[Virginia]]\n|July 3, 1874\n|Grant\n|-\n! style=\"background: {{Republican Party (United States)/meta/color}};\" |{{color|white|28}}\n|[[Marshall Jewell]]\n|[[Connecticut]]\n|August 24, 1874\n|Grant\n|-\n! style=\"