ine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=December 4, 2017}}</ref>\n|5\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Media Control|West German Media Control Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"dechart\">{{cite web\n| url=http://www.officialcharts.de/album.asp?artist=Eagles&title=Hotel+California&cat=a&country=de| title=Album Search: Eagles \u2013 ''Hotel California''| format=ASP|language=German| publisher=Media Control|accessdate=February 10, 2014}}</ref>\n|3\n|}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Year-end charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!Chart (1976)\n!Position\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Australian Albums Chart<ref name=\"auchart\"/>\n|59\n|-\n!Chart (1977)\n!Position\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[List of Top 25 albums for 1977 in Australia|Australian Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"auchart\"/>\n|4\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Austrian Albums Chart<ref>{{cite web|url=http://austriancharts.at/1977_album.asp |title=Austriancharts.at \u2013 Jahreshitparade 1977 |publisher=Hung Medien |language=German |accessdate=July 3, 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140312172539/http://austriancharts.at/1977_album.asp |archivedate=March 12, 2014 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n|12\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[RPM Year-End|Canadian Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"CAYearend77\">{{cite magazine|url=http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-119.01-e.php?brws_s=1&file_num=nlc008388.5558&type=1&interval=24&PHPSESSID=mhe12pta2k83e08udtq66ot062 |title=RPM Top 100 Albums of 1977 |magazine=RPM |date=December 31, 1977 |accessdate=July 3, 2013 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140405134622/http://www.collectionscanada.gc.ca/rpm/028020-119.01-e.php?brws_s=1&file_num=nlc008388.5558&type=1&interval=24&PHPSESSID=mhe12pta2k83e08udtq66ot062 |archivedate=April 5, 2014 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n|2\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Dutch Albums Chart<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dutchcharts.nl/jaaroverzichten.asp?year=1977&cat=a |title=Dutch charts jaaroverzichten 1977|publisher=Dutchcharts.nl |accessdate=April 24, 2014}}</ref>\n|1\n|-\n|a